{"tid":612602,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月新番]水木茂 鬼太郎 第六季 ゲゲゲの鬼太郎  集中討論","createTime":"2018-04-01T03:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T04:51:40.000Z","uid":3020,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9019bdbca8bf1c9301c8de2b1b9668516ea72d18","tid":612602,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Shwimp4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FShwimp4.jpg&h=3bebd9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nゲゲゲの鬼太郎(2018) #01 「妖怪が目覚めた日」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://himado.in/430843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimado.in%2F430843&d=4F49BeM%2Fj3GDFsAwdGZ%2BfUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a55a8df3\" target=\"_blank\">http://himado.in/430843</a><br />\n<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"http://www.toei-anim.co.jp/kitaro/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.toei-anim.co.jp%2Fkitaro%2F&d=4F49BeM%2Fj3GDFsAwdGZ%2BfUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=66382b88\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.toei-anim.co.jp/kitaro/</a><br />\n<br />\n生肉：<a href=\"http://himado.in/?sort=&amp;sortby=&amp;page=0&amp;cat=&amp;click=1&amp;keyword=%E3%82%B2%E3%82%B2%E3%82%B2%E3%81%AE%E9%AC%BC%E5%A4%AA%E9%83%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimado.in%2F%3Fsort%3D%26sortby%3D%26page%3D0%26cat%3D%26click%3D1%26keyword%3D%25E3%2582%25B2%25E3%2582%25B2%25E3%2582%25B2%25E3%2581%25AE%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2583%258E&d=4F49BeM%2Fj3GDFsAwdGZ%2BfUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cf58367c\" target=\"_blank\">http://himado.in/?sort=&amp;sortby=&amp;page=0&amp;cat=&amp;click=1&amp;keyword=%E3%82%B2%E3%82%B2%E3%82%B2%E3%81%AE%E9%AC%BC%E5%A4%AA%E9%83%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n生肉：<a href=\"http://b9good.com/new/157146.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fb9good.com%2Fnew%2F157146.html&d=4F49BeM%2Fj3GDFsAwdGZ%2BfUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=eb5b6823\" target=\"_blank\">http://b9good.com/new/157146.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有鬼怪大師之稱的日本知名作家水木茂，《鬼太郎》為其十分具有代表性的作品。而改編動畫自 1968 年推出至今，已有 50 年的歷史，可說是相當悠久的動畫作品。<br />\n<br />\n　　這次的《鬼太郎》，是以現代作為故事舞台。描述在這個時代，人們已逐漸遺忘妖怪的的存在。但相對的，人們中心的黑暗面以及各種問題的衍生也隨之產生&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原　　作：水木しげる<br />\n製  作  人：狩野雄太、佐川直子、永富大地<br />\n總  導  演：小川孝治<br />\n劇本統籌：大野木寛<br />\n角色設計、作畫導演：清水空翔<br />\n音　　樂：高梨康治、刃 - yaiba-<br />\n動畫製作：フジテレビ・読売広告社・東映アニメーション<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n鬼  太  郎：澤城美雪<br />\n眼珠老爹：野澤雅子<br />\n鼠　　男：古川登志夫<br />\n貓　　女：庄司宇芽香<br />\n犬山真奈：藤井幸代<br />\n撒砂婆婆：田中真弓</div><br />\n子泣爺爺、塗壁：島田敏<br />\n一反木棉：山口勝平"},{"pid":"3eb625ecc6aae47ac07475b7941540d419af28a0","tid":612602,"uid":146051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"0e036f8b211165a7c3dbab362de75bbd0940dfe2","tid":612602,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43552-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-43552-1-1.html&d=4F49BeM%2Fj3GDFsAwdGZ%2BfUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=eb87bcb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43552-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"714bcc6d6c912df4f478f5dc62de39baa0cd9b75","tid":612602,"uid":17637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"感謝樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f2d280f0c866523ce24995b69a94ab3796a2e0","tid":612602,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:48:37.000Z","msg":"Thx 台主😭"},{"pid":"6759e9906e8f7fcc1ae114cb10a3a7890210dc5d","tid":612602,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"鬼太郎型左, <span style=\"co